      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <h3>Santa Monica, Scotsman Prodigy ELITE C1030A cube (2017 install)</h3>
        <p>Hotel. Refrigerant slow leak. Hotel had been refilling every 3 months (previous shop violating EPA 608 Section 608 leak-repair-before-recharge rule). EPA 608 leak detection: brazed evap joint repair, evacuated, recharged R-404A. Now compliant. Total: $120 plus $480 refrigerant plus $720 labor plus leak detection = $1,420.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
