        <p>Hospital cafeteria. Multi-component service: spray pump plus scale buildup plus water filter overdue. Standard cleaning plus spray pump replacement plus new water filter. Total: $120 plus $280 cleaning plus $440 spray pump plus $160 filter = $1,000.</p>
